The Teeny-tiny Atari 2600 demo (2026)
Released Thursday, July 16, 2026.
4K / 4096-byte NTSC Atari 2600 demo.
Four title scenes with raster bars, stars,
checker grids, bouncing sprites and ticker.
Take On Me TIA soundtrack, derived from
Jukebox by Lloyd Russell; published in
Your Sinclair issue 21, September 1987,
for the ZX Spectrum 128K.
Automatic demo; no controls.
Run in Stella.
